  "detailed_description": "Gooper is a challenging 2D puzzle game. Work your way through 200 levels with escalating difficulty and mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/e035e9ec722d1044437797b7b107442c.poster.avif?t=1732727098\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/e035e9ec722d1044437797b7b107442c.webm?t=1732727098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/e035e9ec722d1044437797b7b107442c.mp4?t=1732727098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Help Gooper, the frictionless blob, get to the exit of the maze by slinging him between various obstacles. Don't forget to collect Gooper's missing Goo-bits along the way!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Massive selection of 200 levels across 8 level packs.<br></li><li>Wide range of interconnecting mechanics, escalating the challenge of the puzzles to new levels.<br></li><li> Control Gooper with either keyboard, mouse, touch or controller.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/d726e622755fe01b7db347b37ea9ee44.poster.avif?t=1732727098\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/d726e622755fe01b7db347b37ea9ee44.webm?t=1732727098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/d726e622755fe01b7db347b37ea9ee44.mp4?t=1732727098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Gooper is a challenging 2D puzzle game. Work your way through 200 levels with escalating difficulty and mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/e035e9ec722d1044437797b7b107442c.poster.avif?t=1732727098\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/e035e9ec722d1044437797b7b107442c.webm?t=1732727098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/e035e9ec722d1044437797b7b107442c.mp4?t=1732727098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Help Gooper, the frictionless blob, get to the exit of the maze by slinging him between various obstacles. Don't forget to collect Gooper's missing Goo-bits along the way!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Massive selection of 200 levels across 8 level packs.<br></li><li>Wide range of interconnecting mechanics, escalating the challenge of the puzzles to new levels.<br></li><li> Control Gooper with either keyboard, mouse, touch or controller.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/d726e622755fe01b7db347b37ea9ee44.poster.avif?t=1732727098\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/d726e622755fe01b7db347b37ea9ee44.webm?t=1732727098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1559620/extras/d726e622755fe01b7db347b37ea9ee44.mp4?t=1732727098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
